@NODE "HISTORY" "Wizard-Handler User Documentation"
@TOC "CONTENTS"

    Miscellaneous / History


It took over one year of part-time effort to understand Sharp's
documentation well enough to write this handler.  Wizard-Handler began as a
quick hack, evolved into a Shell-based tool, then to a simple handler.  I
then attempted to re-write it as a device but found that too restrictive
and put more effort into the handler.

Version       Comment

0.1 - 2.0     Private releases.
2.x           Releases shared with Matt Simmons.
3.0           First public release.

@ENDNODE
